"Thanks, I'll move forward to get a better view. I see a purple ball in front of me, but no box yet."
"Keep moving forward, I'll follow and try to get around the wall to our left, maybe the box is behind it."
"Alright, I'll take another step forward. Ah, I see the wall is quite close, I'll try to move left to get around it."
"Good call, I'll mirror your move and go left as well, let's see if we can find the box together."
